&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;18emtuw&quot; data-start=&quot;1061&quot; data-end=&quot;1180&quot;&gt;Ensure carrier compliance with DOT regulations, permitting requirements, and customer-specific service expectations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1k4lrhk&quot; data-start=&quot;1181&quot; data-end=&quot;1266&quot;&gt;Negotiate pricing and secure competitive carrier solutions for heavy haul freight&lt;/li&gt;
